14 panels and batteries used in the commonwealth, including but not limited to anticipated life
15 cycles; (iv) anticipated infrastructure needs, including but not limited to transportation of
16 materials; (v) emerging technologies; (vi) potential scaled manufacturer or installer stewardship
17 programs; (vii) anticipated costs to implement the plan; (viii) statutory recommendations, if any;
18 and (ix) other matters pertaining to solar panel and battery decommissioning and stewardship, in
